videos.description: Samford running back Roland Adams punches it in for another score for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Samford goes up 13-0 against Florida State

videos.description: Florida State wide receiver Tamorrion Terry hauls the ball in with one hand and scores a 27-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Seminoles get on board with 27-yard TD

videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois runs for an 8-yard score to put the Seminoles down 2 against Samford.
videos.headline: Francois keeps it himself for 8-yard score

videos.description: Samford's Devlin Hodges airs it out to wide receiver Kelvin McKnight for a 27-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Samford strikes again

videos.description: Florida State wide receiver Tamorrion Terry reels in his second touchdown of the game right before halftime.
videos.headline: Florida State scores right before half

videos.description: Florida State Deondre Francois connects with Tre' McKitty for a 5-yard score and then Nyqwan Murray for the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Francois saves Seminoles with go-ahead TD, 2-point conversion

videos.description: Florida State defensive back Levonta Taylor returns a 63-yard interception to put the Seminoles up by 9.
videos.headline: FSU's pick-6 puts the nail in the coffin
